data.value:
~Version 1.0.0.2~ 1. Added Vmium option.
~Version 1.0.0.1~ 1. Bug fixes and performance improvements.
~Version 1.0.0.0~ 1. Added ability to set a custom background. 2. Added ability to set a custom colour. 3. Fixed a bug that would cause an exception at start-up. 4. Fixed a bug that would cause the Messages button to navigate to Notifications. 5. Added ability to go directly to a user's profile.
~Version 0.5.0.0~ (We're in Beta!) 1. Added Settings Panel. 2. Added ability to set whether to minimise to system tray or to taskbar. 3. Added ability to make the application full screen. 4. Added ability to change how the application starts. 5. Added ability to start an OBS Widget for streams. 6. Added ability to set profile for native access. 7. Fixed a bug where notification toasts wouldn't show if you had more than one pending notification.
~Version 0.2.0.0~ 1. Added New Window option. 2. Title now shows where you are on the website. 3. Added system tray icon and menu. 4. Application now minimises to system tray by default. 5. Added a red dot when user has pending notifications. 6. Added notification when you have pending notifications.
~Version 0.1.0.0~ 1. Initial Alpha.
